Q1: How did you prioritize testing?

👉 I prioritized payroll functionality first because salary accuracy is business-critical and directly impacts employees.

Q2: What testing approach did you follow?

👉 I used exploratory testing, functional testing, and negative testing to identify real-world edge cases and system failures.

Q3: Why did you include automation?

👉 To ensure repeatability and enable faster regression testing for critical HRMS workflows.

Q4: What was the biggest risk?

👉 Incorrect payroll calculation or attendance miscalculation leading to salary errors.
